          class="container"
          style="
            position: absolute;
            width: 650px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: white;
          "
        >
          <h3 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 40px">
            Man must explore, and this is exploration at its greatest
          </h3>
          <p style="font-size: 15px">Creado por Marty Mcfly el 24 de setiembre, 2022</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <article style="height: 500px" class="container border-bottom mt-5">
      <p class="mb-4">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequuntur exercitationem,
